headline: CarMax downgraded by Morgan Stanley amid execution woes and leadership uncertainty
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley has downgraded CarMax (NYSE: KMX) to Equal-weight from Overweight in a note on Monday and slashed its price target to $35 from $56, citing “degradation in execution and uncertainty around new leadership” as key risks during a critical transition period.
